Steps to run the Test file and to find Accuracy
--------------------------------------------------

# config.yaml defines the path to input, output and module directories

# to train
# relevant files taken from the config file

$ python train.py

# to test/predict
# relevant files taken from the config file

$ python modules/mod_test.py

# to measure the accuracy
# <true_label_filename> should be put in the input directory, as configured in config.yaml

$ python modules/mod_accuracy.py <true_label_filename>

-----------------------------------------
Lambda  Accuracy

10**-4      0.9952
10**-5      0.9954
10**-6      0.9954
10**-7      0.9954
10**-8      0.9954
10**-9      0.9954
10**-10    0.9956
------------------------------------------

10**-10 gave the best accuracy